          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">Carbon monoxide poisoning in Georgia</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/ps-dec-18-2.png" alt="Carbon monoxide poisoning in Georgia" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px);">Eleven Indian nationals and one Georgian were found <a href="https://www.dw.com/en/georgia-11-indians-found-dead-at-gudauri-ski-resort/a-71081207" target="_blank">dead</a> at a <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Gudauri,+Georgia/@42.4758858,44.4611023,15z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m10!1m2!2m1!1sgudauri+ski+resort!3m6!1s0x404528fdf2ee8197:0xf2c31d07053611a4!8m2!3d42.4755394!4d44.4804723!15sChJndWRhdXJpIHNraSByZXNvcnSSAQhsb2NhbGl0eeABAA!16zL20vMDhyajJw?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI0MTIxMS4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D" target="_blank">Gudauri</a> ski resort in Georgia, reportedly due to suspected carbon monoxide poisoning. The victims, believed to be workers at an Indian restaurant, were discovered in a commercial building where an oil-powered generator had been turned on following a power outage. Authorities indicated that the generator was placed dangerously close to an indoor area, accumulating carbon monoxide.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px);">
          The Indian embassy in Tbilisi expressed deep condolences and assured it is working with local authorities to repatriate the victims' remains to India. The embassy also contacts the bereaved families to provide necessary support. Preliminary investigations found no signs of violence, and officials continued to assess the incident to confirm the exact cause of death.</p>
        </mj-text>
